   <title type="text">BODO : Bibel+Orient Datenbank Online</title>
   <content type="html"><![CDATA[<a href="http://www.bible-orient-museum.ch/bodo/">BODO : Bibel+Orient Datenbank Online</a><br /><blockquote class="tr_bq"><img alt="http://www.bible-orient-museum.ch/bodo/_imgs/BODO_title_small.png" class="decoded" height="79" src="http://www.bible-orient-museum.ch/bodo/_imgs/BODO_title_small.png" width="320" /> </blockquote><blockquote class="tr_bq"><span style="font-size: x-small;">The BIBLE+ORIENT Museum Database is a&nbsp;<em>web based database created for the electronic management of ancient Near Eastern image and object data</em>.  The numerous data fields enable not only a precise cataloging of the  museum inventory but also systematic searches for purposes of scientific  research. Furthermore, the database admits the consultation of  digitalized catalogs of the collections, the management of image series  (e.g. slide shows), the making available of dynamic e-Learning content  and the fast creation of PowerPoint presentations as well as  publications.</span><br /> <span style="font-size: x-small;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: x-small;">The user has at his disposal images in an unlimited amount of views  for each object, each in the following four formats: thumbnail, normal  size, PowerPoint format and print resolution.</span><br /> <span style="font-size: x-small;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: x-small;">The idea of an internet database allows not only world wide access  but also stimulates the cooperation between partners who want to share  the data with one another. The database was designed so that image and  object data from an unlimited number of institutions and private persons  can be managed. Currently, we are working on national, European and  global levels to include into our database objects from other  iconographically relevant collections as well.</span></blockquote><blockquote class="tr_bq"><ul class="menu_article"><li class="menu_article active">           <a href="http://www.bible-orient-museum.ch/index.php/en/collections/online-database-bodo">               <span style="font-size: x-small;">Database              </span></a><span style="font-size: x-small;">        </span></li><li class="menu_article ">           <span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://www.bible-orient-museum.ch/index.php/en/collections/online-database-bodo/148-verwendungsmoeglichkeiten">               Applications              </a></span>        </li><li class="menu_article ">           <span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://www.bible-orient-museum.ch/index.php/en/collections/online-database-bodo/144-technische-daten">               Technical Data              </a></span>        </li><li class="menu_article ">           <span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://www.bible-orient-museum.ch/index.php/en/collections/online-database-bodo/145-funktionsumfang">               Functional Range              </a></span>        </li><li class="menu_article ">           <span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://www.bible-orient-museum.ch/index.php/en/collections/online-database-bodo/146-implementierungsstatus">               Implementation Status              </a></span>        </li><li class="menu_article ">           <span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://www.bible-orient-museum.ch/index.php/en/collections/online-database-bodo/187-bodo">               BODO              </a></span>        </li></ul></blockquote><blockquote class="tr_bq"></blockquote>]]></content>
